commit.message:
cccp.c (print_help): Fix typos.

        * cccp.c (print_help): Fix typos.
        * cpplib.c (print_help): Fix typos.
        * toplev.c (f_optiosn): Fix typos.
        (documented_lang_options): Fix typos.

From-SVN: r24706

+	* cpplib.c (print_help): Fix typos.
+	* toplev.c (f_optiosn): Fix typos.
